snippet.title: Ashu Bagri
snippet.description: Welcome to my Youtube channel-"Ashu Bagri", where you will find views of mine on the stocks, stock market and nifty prediction of  India for investing for beginners, pop it, day trading, learning for stock market for beginners to earn money, by doing Technical Analysis. how to beat the stock market is my main motto. Coming out with stock market and nifty prediction  video at the weekend or the weeknd. No news for analysis but only charts. Watching new film, movies, song, music, video in free time. Sometimes come live also. Like the Kapil Sharma show, and sometimes watch CNBC and Aaj Tak live on tv. Want to travel around the world not today or now ,but when I earn money in stock market. Staying in Mumbai or Delhi sometimes. Looking for jobs in company .Doing Business of Finance in stock market to earn money. Now a days many girl and woman have come in stock market. how to create a YouTube channel was easy for me .best ever food review show I saw was that of Taste of Rajasthan resta

hi_IN.title: Ashu Bagri
hi_IN.description: Ashu Bagri ,Technical Analyst staying sometimes in Mumbai, Delhi and Rajasthan and doing job in stock market of India. Doing Technical Analysis of the new Company stocks listed on NSE { National Stock Exchange of India} and BSE Stock exchanges Like to do  live, best and latest Analysis of Nifty share price, Bank Nifty share price Nifty 50, Sensex, BSE Sensex and Sensex today  in share market for Indian people and Investors  who wants to apply Finance for Investment and also for Stock Trader in share who do trade in day trading for money. Learning today how to review trade on Foreign Exchange Market of World on mobile app. Learning stock market for beginners and basics of stock market for beginners very easy on this channel. I like Film, movie, music, song, news, gaming, comedy, video show on stock or share of 2021 on zee and Aaj Tak tv. No investment of mine in the stock market of India 🇮🇳.
